    new "Sarah followed Eula out of their cell."

    old "Leading through the hallways, they soon arrived at the mess hall."
    new "Leading through the hallways, they soon arrived at the mess hall."

    old "Sarah made sure to stay close to Eula."
    new "Sarah made sure to stay close to Eula."

    old "In a strange and dangerous place like this, it felt like the only security she could cling to."
    new "In a strange and dangerous place like this, it felt like the only security she could cling to."

    old "Eula by contrast seemed to walk with an air of confidence, clearly more experienced at prison life."
