    new "Sarah looked in the direction and saw a group of three women."

    old "Yeah, I see them."
    new "Yeah, I see them."

    old "That's Synara and her cronies."
    new "That's Synara and her cronies."

    old "They're trouble, try and steer clear of them if you can."
    new "They're trouble, try and steer clear of them if you can."

