    new "Sarah could imagine what she meant. Not that she had much experience with romance."

    old "Still, it all felt awfully transactional. She struggled to imagine that she could ever view it as casually as Eula did."
    new "Still, it all felt awfully transactional. She struggled to imagine that she could ever view it as casually as Eula did."

